summary: This simple batch file adds all of the books in Skyrim to the player\'s inventory.
descriptionHtml: The file adds all books, including skill books to the player\'s inventory.  Spell tomes are NOT included, only readable books, skill books, and those that start quests.  There are a large number of books, so you will most likely become overencumbered upon executing the command.  I will update as needed, if an update is needed.  Enjoy!
author: mtudor456
